 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完全無求證精神</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n駛鬼求證？<br />\n你覺得社會無呢d事？<br />\n係真係假原意都係想講香港真係有好多垃圾會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f49ee5e2614ab1ffea5094c999e4be15301e801e","tid":190224,"uid":36025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T04:28:46.000Z","msg":"樓上已經講左假新聞<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 再者綜援係保障部批唔撚係社署<br />\n做嘢個班都唔一定係社工，早排先有荀工保障部助招聘<br />\n<br />\n成班得個屌但又無啲知識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c14ab7a7f2b5160a86c6b10b2a1470ccb35c4feb","tid":190224,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T04:29:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>不知名網站<br />\n假新聞？</blockquote><br />\n係<br />\n連登啲小學雞真係低質到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完全無求證精神</blockquote><br />\n係你老母<br />\n舊聞姐唔係假新聞<br />\n咩求證精神呀你</blockquote><br />\n你對眼重廢過屎眼"},{"pid":"5d02c880de6e63909498931b2c1de70a3896a87b","tid":190224,"uid":55,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T04:36:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"db04d23b0435712634f5b9edf718988f099b1a7c","tid":190224,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T04:37:09.000Z","msg":"住現崇山都拎倒綜援啦，呢d碎料啦！"}]}